quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  52,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  52,1,( kohay ) tor ki qasam
  52,2,aur kitaab ki jo likhi hui hai
  52,3,kushadah ourak mein
  52,4,aur abad ghar ki
  52,5,aur onche chhat ki
  52,6,aur ublatey hue darya ki
  52,7,ke tumahray perwar-digaar ka azaab waqay ho kar rahay ga
  52,8,( aur ) is ko koi rok nahi sakay ga
  52,9,jis din aasman larazne laga kpkpa kar
  52,10,aur pahar urnay lagey oon ho kar
  52,11,is din jhutlanay walon ke liye kharabi hai
  52,12,jo khoz ( baatil ) mein parre khail rahay hain
  52,13,jis din un ko aatish jahannum ki taraf dhakel dhakel kar le jayen ge
  52,14,yahi woh jahannum hai jis ko tum jhoot samajte they
  52,15,tokiya yeh jaadoo hai ya tum ko nazar hi nahi aata
  52,16,is mein daakhil hojao aur sabr karo ya nah karo tumahray liye yaksaa hai. jo kaam tumkiya karte they ( yeh ) unhi ka tum ko badla mil raha hai
  52,17,jo parhaizgaar hain woh baghoon aur nematon mein hon ge
  52,18,jo kuch un ke perwar-digaar ne un ko bakhsha is ( ki wajah ) se khushaal. aur un ke perwar-digaar ne un ko dozakh ke azaab se bacha liya
  52,19,apne aamaal ke siilay mein mazay se khao aur piyo
  52,20,takhton par jo barabar barabar bchhe hue hain takiya lagaye hue aur barri barri aankhon wali hurron se hum un ka Aqab kar den ge
  52,21,aur jo log imaan laaye aur un ki aulaad bhi ( raah ) imaan mein un ke peechay chali. hum un ki aulaad ko bhi un ( ke darjay ) taq pouncha den ge aur un ke aamaal mein se kuch kam nah karen ge. har shakhs apne aamaal mein phansa howa hai
  52,22,aur jis terhan ke meway aur gosht ko un ka jee chahay ga hum un ko ataa karen ge
  52,23,wahan woh aik dosray se jaam sharaab jhapat liya karen ge jis ( ke peenay ) se nah haziyan saraai hogi nah koi gunah ki baat
  52,24,aur nojawan khidmat gaar ( jo aisay hon ge ) jaisay chupaye hue moti un ke aas paas phrin ge
  52,25,aur aik dosray ki taraf rukh karkay aapas mein guftagu karen ge
  52,26,kahin ge ke is se pehlay hum apne ghar mein ( khuda se ) drtay rehtay they
  52,27,to khuda ne hum par ahsaan farmaya aur hamein lau ke azaab se bacha liya
  52,28,is se pehlay hum is se duayenkiya karte they. be shak woh ahsaan karne wala meharban hai
  52,29,to ( ae paighambar ) tum nasiyaat karte raho tum apne perwar-digaar ke fazl se nah to کاہن ho aur nah deewany
  52,30,kiya kafir kehte hain ke yeh shayar hai ( aur ) hum is ke haq mein zamane ke hawadis ka intzaar kar rahay hain
  52,31,keh do ke intzaar kiye jao mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon
  52,32,kiya un ki aqlain un ko yahi sikhati hain. balkay yeh log hain hi shareer
  52,33,kiya ( kufar ) kehte hain ke un paighambar ne quran az khud bana liya hai baat yeh hai ke yeh ( khuda par ) imaan nahi rakhtay
  52,34,agar yeh sachey hain to aisa kalaam bana to layein
  52,35,kiya yeh kisi ke peda kiye baghair hi peda hogaye hain. ya yeh khud ( apne tain ) peda karne walay hain
  52,36,ya unhon ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya hai? ( nahi ) balkay yeh yaqeen hi nahi rakhtay
  52,37,kiya un ke paas tumahray perwar-digaar ke khazanay hain. ya yeh ( kahin ke ) Darogha hain ?
  52,38,ya un ke paas koi seerhi hai jis par ( charh kar aasman se baatein ) sun atay hain. to jo sun aata hai woh Sarih sanad dukhaay
  52,39,kiya khuda ki to betiyan aur tumahray betay
  52,40,( ae paighambar )kiya tum un se sila mangte ho ke un par tawwan ka boojh par raha hai
  52,41,ya un ke paas ghaib ( ka ilm ) hai ke woh usay likh letay hain
  52,42,kiya yeh koi daon karna chahtay hain to kafir to khud daon mein anay walay hain
  52,43,kiya khuda ke siwa un ka koi aur mabood hai? khuda un ke shareek bananay se pak hai
  52,44,aur agar yeh aasman se ( azaab ) ka koi tukda girta howa dekhen to kahin ke yeh gaarha baadal hai
  52,45,"pas un ko chore do yahan taq ke woh roz jis mein woh be hosh kardiye jayen ge, samnay aajay"
  52,46,jis din un ka koi daon kuch bhi kaam nah aeye aur nah un ko ( kahin se ) madad hi miley
  52,47,aur zaalmon ke liye is ke siwa aur azaab bhi hai lekin un mein ke aksar nahi jantay
  52,48,aur tum apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke intzaar mein sabr kiye raho. tum to hamari aankhon ke samnay ho aur jab uttha karo to apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeehkiya karo
  52,49,aur raat ke baaz auqaat mein bhi aur sitaron ke ghuroob honay ke baad bhi is ki تنزیہkiya karo
